<body>
  <h1 class="ok">User written to .env</h1>
  <p>For account <strong>{{ user_email }}</strong>, the <code>ADMINS</code> variable was added to <code>.env</code> with a password hash.</p>
  <p><strong>Restart the application</strong> so the process reloads the environment and imports the user into the database (when <code>cms_users</code> is empty, this happens on startup).</p>
  <p>For example:</p>
  <pre><code>sudo systemctl restart demo-cms</code></pre>
  <p>After restart, open <a href="/cms/login">/cms/login</a> and sign in with the same email and password.</p>
</body>
